It was the first and last time anyone attempted to levy a tax on the <mark>witches</mark> of Dunbarrow.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/d/3d2d5a71-d6e1-4c96-9a53-0e370047a56e.jpg?1782696654"}, {"card": "Ardent Elementalist", "set": "MID", "html": "While the Dawnhart <mark>witches</mark> focus their magic on nature and community, other covens consort with devils and twist the elements to their will.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/5/f58592f7-1df5-428d-9dde-e6acd9a5d1d5.jpg?1782703652"}, {"card": "Hex Magic", "set": "MSH", "html": "At the Scarlet <mark>Witch</mark>&#x27;s touch, probabilities shift and the impossible becomes real.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/2/5/259bed47-1950-43ae-8efd-3009537529a8.jpg?1782681802"}, {"card": "Bog Initiate", "set": "INV", "html": "&quot;Urborg&#x27;s magic is strong. Did Urza send you to protect us or to protect against us?&quot;\n—Urborg <mark>witch</mark>, to Barrin", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/9/8962dc3b-24ca-4c3c-ba1d-933c29cf7b73.jpg?1782720053"}, {"card": "Might of the Old Ways", "set": "MID", "html": "Brimming with power from their disrupted ritual, the Dawnhart <mark>witches</mark> lashed out at the werewolf intruders.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/a/6a853679-e9dd-4c05-8688-248de8f12760.jpg?1782703607"}, {"card": "Eerie Interference", "set": "WOE", "html": "Ranks of sleeping Ardenvale knights filled Eriette&#x27;s throne room, ready to defend their <mark>witch</mark>-queen with unthinking devotion.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/4/2/42a74545-75c8-4a6b-bee1-ac5665d9bcf0.jpg?1782696652"}, {"card": "Addle", "set": "VMA", "html": "&quot;I&#x27;ll wring out your tiny mind like a sponge.&quot;\n—Urborg <mark>witch</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/7/f7fcce83-4378-405f-8007-dd0ed002be6b.jpg?1782751432"}, {"card": "Technomancer", "set": "40K", "html": "&quot;<mark>Witchcraft</mark> or technology, it is blasphemous, and it must be stopped.&quot;\n—Inquisitor Greyfax", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/1/c160c1f7-714e-444a-ab74-c64c3a099a48.jpg?1782700177"}, {"card": "Malevolent Noble", "set": "ELD", "html": "He has slain a dozen <mark>witches</mark>, luring each with a promise of fresh children&#x27;s bones.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/b/6bc7e996-151f-4d88-8e1e-91bb88f5db02.jpg?1782707871"}, {"card": "Agadeem's Awakening // Agadeem, the Undercrypt", "set": "ZNR", "html": "&quot;Now is the death-hour, just before dawn. Wake, sleepers, and haunt the living!&quot;\n—Vivias, <mark>Witch</mark> Vessel\n&quot;Here below the hedron fields, souls and secrets lie entombed.&quot;\n—Vivias, <mark>Witch</mark> Vessel", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/7/67f4c93b-080c-4196-b095-6a120a221988.jpg?1782706316"}, {"card": "Festering Newt", "set": "JMP", "html": "Its back bubbles like a <mark>witch</mark>&#x27;s cauldron, and it smells just as vile.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/c/9/c9d7d31e-eaa7-4edf-8e98-5a191ec3b91d.jpg?1782706636"}, {"card": "Turn to Mist", "set": "CLU", "html": "&quot;Did you expect me to dodge? How quaint.&quot;\n—Olka, mistmeadow <mark>witch</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/b/8be0076c-3f9c-4120-b768-4e8985ee6a7c.jpg?1782693453"}, {"card": "Ox Drover", "set": "WOC", "html": "&quot;Ho, Shaggyfoot! Lumpton, pick up those hooves! Edgewall by sundown or I&#x27;ll sell the lot of you to a <mark>witch</mark>!&quot;", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/4/b479be78-da22-41f0-937e-348dc0c7511e.jpg?1782696378"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Cursebound Witch", "set": "YMID", "html": "When Cursebound <mark>Witch</mark> dies, draft a card from Cursebound <mark>Witch</mark>&#x27;s spellbook."}, {"card": "Witch-king of Angmar", "set": "LTR", "html": "Discard a card: <mark>Witch</mark>-king of Angmar gains indestructible until end of turn. Tap it."}, {"card": "The Vision and Scarlet Witch", "set": "MSC", "html": "Flying\nWhenever you cast a spell, add {R} and put a +1/+1 counter on The Vision and Scarlet <mark>Witch</mark>."}, {"card": "Celestine Cave Witch", "set": "CMB2", "html": "When Celestine Cave <mark>Witch</mark> enters, create two 1/1 black Insect creature tokens."}, {"card": "Festering Newt", "set": "JMP", "html": "When this creature dies, target creature an opponent controls gets -1/-1 until end of turn. That creature gets -4/-4 instead if you control a creature named Bogbrew <mark>Witch</mark>."}, {"card": "Kindly Stranger // Demon-Possessed Witch", "set": "SOI", "html": "Delirium — {2}{B}: Transform this creature. Activate only if there are four or more card types among cards in your graveyard.\nWhen this creature transforms into Demon-Possessed <mark>Witch</mark>, you may destroy target creature."}, {"card": "Tasha, the Witch Queen", "set": "CLB", "html": "Tasha, the <mark>Witch</mark> Queen can be your commander."}, {"card": "Scarlet Witch, Chaotic Avenger", "set": "MSC", "html": "Whenever Scarlet <mark>Witch</mark> deals combat damage to a player, look at the top two cards of your library, then exile them face down. Then you may cast a Hero or noncreature spell from among cards exiled with Scarlet <mark>Witch</mark> without paying its mana cost."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/6/0685afcb-06f6-4d18-b8c2-510764558dc1.jpg?1782696544", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/0/6/0685afcb-06f6-4d18-b8c2-510764558dc1.jpg?1782696544", "card": "Witch's Mark"}}